originalText.text:
Who knew such a beautiful dream could spawn from the loss of a beautiful child!! Great work is being done, and lives are being touched the same way AJ touched ours. Strength, Hope, and Light is what is being offered to the community... Classes, events, and resources to the most vulnerable... One step at a time, but it’s getting done.
Please take a moment to visit the website, leave a comment, leave a review, contact the founder if you need any help. Donate and contribute to any of the events, or just for the cause. Let’s continue to make this what it can be...
Peace and Light!!
